      <title>法官批准司法部发布特朗普 2020 年大选案件报告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/judge-clears-release-of-trump-special-counsel-report-on-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州的一名联邦法官不会阻止美国司法部长梅里克·加兰德 (Merrick Garland) 公布针对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的联邦刑事调查的最终报告的部分内容。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/judge-clears-release-of-trump-special-counsel-report-on-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 17:43:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
