      <title>哥伦比亚财政部长称左翼领导人不能吓跑投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/finance-chief-seeks-to-soothe-colombia-investors-over-debt-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚新​​任财政部长迭戈·格瓦拉表示，哥伦比亚政府致力于保持公共债务可持续发展并保持投资者信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/finance-chief-seeks-to-soothe-colombia-investors-over-debt-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 17:17:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国授权军方击落神秘无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/germany-authorizes-military-to-shoot-down-mysterious-drones</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，德国正在赋予其武装部队击落涉嫌监视军事基地、工业设施和其他关键基础设施的不明无人机的能力。]]></description>
