    <item>
      <title>波士顿市长重启推动房主减税计划 应对税费激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/boston-mayor-revives-push-for-homeowner-tax-relief-as-bills-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波士顿市长米歇尔吴 (Michelle Wu) 正试图重启一项失败的努力，以减轻因房产税两位数增长而遭受的房主的负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/boston-mayor-revives-push-for-homeowner-tax-relief-as-bills-jump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>小唐纳德·特朗普加入卡尔什并炒作选举投注市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/donald-trump-jr-joins-kalshi-and-hypes-market-for-election-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump Jr.) 担任预测市场 Kalshi 的顾问，将该博彩网站和其他类似网站打造为评估政治和选举状况的优质来源。]]></description>
