      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:53:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登债务减免计划帮助的学生贷款借款人超过 500 万</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/student-loan-borrowers-aided-by-biden-debt-relief-tops-5-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登周一采取行动，免除超过 15 万人的联邦学生贷款，作为最后一搏，这将使在他执政期间获得贷款减免的借款人总数超过 500 万人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/student-loan-borrowers-aided-by-biden-debt-relief-tops-5-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:33:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾伯塔省省长警告称，特朗普的关税即将到来，将包括石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/alberta-premier-warns-trump-tariffs-coming-including-on-oil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿尔伯塔省省长丹尼尔·史密斯在佛罗里达会见美国当选总统后警告称，一旦唐纳德·特朗普下周就任总统，加拿大人应该准备好面对美国关税，石油产品将不会受到豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/alberta-premier-warns-trump-tariffs-coming-including-on-oil</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯洛伐克总统菲科提议与泽连斯基会面以恢复天然气供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/slovakia-s-fico-floats-zelenskiy-meeting-on-resuming-gas-transit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年年初，基辅与莫斯科之间的协议到期后，斯洛伐克总理罗伯特·菲佐邀请乌克兰总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基就恢复天然气运输进行会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/slovakia-s-fico-floats-zelenskiy-meeting-on-resuming-gas-transit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 16:10:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默对里夫斯“充满信心”，支持财政规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/starmer-has-full-confidence-in-reeves-stresses-fiscal-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默表示，他对财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯“充满信心”，并强调英国政府将坚持财政规则，以应对英国借贷成本飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/starmer-has-full-confidence-in-reeves-stresses-fiscal-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 13:12:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
